<p><b>What does BSC MLT stand for?</b> The full form of B.Sc. MLT is Bachelor of Science in Medical Laboratory Technology.</p>
<p><b>What is the first semester of BSC MLT?</b> The first semester of the course includes Human Physiology I and Human Anatomy II, with biochemistry as a BSc MLT subject. The second semester comprises Human anatomy II, Human Physiology II, and a practical workshop.</p>
