<p><b>What is microbiology in MLT?</b> About the programme: The MSc MLT in Medical Microbiology is an allied health profession that specializes in micro- organisms that cause disease. The role of the technologist in this field is to aid the doctor or medical microbiologist in detecting, diagnosing, and preventing diseases through clinical laboratory tests.</p>
